%section.sign-up
  .row
    .span4
      %h4.blue Sign up
      = render partial: 'form', locals: {resource: resource, button_text: 'Sign up'} 
    .span8
      %header.subhead
        %h1.jumbotron Create a FastRego account today!
      %p 
        A FastRego account will enable you to sign your university contingent up for any FastRego run tournament registration. 
      %p 
        Beside making registration painless, we are also planning many other features such as
        %ul
          %li A profile page for all participants that will allow you to keep track of the tournaments you have participated in over the years
          %li A record of all your scoring and how you have fared in tournaments 
